  "remarks": "\nElvira NABIULLINA is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because NABIULLINA is obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia through working for the Government of Russia as Governor of the Central Bank of the Russian Federation.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
